        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>你好！这是一个博客测试页面</p><p>代码块测试</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (MenuFlag == MenuMode) &#123; <span class="comment">//菜单模式</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">switch</span> (EncoderState) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">case</span> PageDowm:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (CurrenMenu-&gt;next != <span class="literal">NULL</span>) CurrenMenu = CurrenMenu-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">    EncoderState = NoScroll;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">case</span> PageUp:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (CurrenMenu-&gt;prev != <span class="literal">NULL</span>) CurrenMenu = CurrenMenu-&gt;prev;</span><br><span class="line">    EncoderState = NoScroll;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">case</span> NoScroll:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">switch</span> (KeyPressType) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">case</span> KeyShortPress:</span><br><span class="line">      KeyPressType = KeyNoPress;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> (CurrenMenu-&gt;child != <span class="literal">NULL</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        CurrenMenu = CurrenMenu-&gt;child;</span><br><span class="line">        select = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (CurrenMenu-&gt;Execute != <span class="literal">NULL</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        MenuFlag = EditMode;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">continue</span>; <span class="comment">//立即重新循环，防止画面抽搐</span></span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">case</span> KeyDoublePress:</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span> (CurrenMenu-&gt;parent != <span class="literal">NULL</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        CurrenMenu = CurrenMenu-&gt;parent;</span><br><span class="line">        select = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      KeyPressType = KeyNoPress;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">default</span>:</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  CurrenMenu-&gt;OLED_Display();</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (MenuFlag == EditMode) &#123; <span class="comment">//编辑模式</span></span><br><span class="line">      CurrenMenu-&gt;Execute();</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">/* USER CODE END WHILE */</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">/* USER CODE BEGIN 3 */</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
